737 INDUSTRIAL ENGINEERING MANAGER
Professional Summary
Self-motivated, innovative and goal-oriented Industrial Engineer, Project Manager and Team Leader dedicated to boosting company revenue
through exceptional leadership and rigorous cost and schedule control techniques. Desires the opportunity to revamp processes and procedures
and increase efficiency and product quality.
